The '''rlm_always''' module enables some debugging.

{{Default in the server source|src/modules/rlm_always/}}

==Configuration==

{{Default in the server source|raddb/modules/always}}

<pre>
	#
	# The "always" module is here for debugging purposes. Each
	# instance simply returns the same result, always, without
	# doing anything.
	always fail {
		rcode = fail
	}
	always reject {
		rcode = reject
	}
	always ok {
		rcode = ok
		simulcount = 0
		mpp = no
	}
</pre>